# Notification Failures
# 
# Tests how the script handles SMS notification failures.
# 
# Mock Endpoint:
# Simulate a failing API endpoint by using a URL that times out or responds with an error (e.g., `http://localhost:9999`).
# 
# Expected Behavior:
#   - The script logs errors when trying to send SMS notifications.
#   - Continues monitoring the API endpoint.
# 
# Test command:
# `../check_endpoint.sh > notification_failures.log 2>&1`
# 
# Verify:
#   - Check the logs for the notification failure messages:
#     `grep "Failed to send SMS" notification_failures.log`
# 
HASS_API_URL="http://localhost:9999"  # Unreachable URL
HASS_AUTH_TOKEN="valid_token"
SMS_TO="+1234567890"
SMS_FROM="sender@example.com"
NOTIFICATION_PROVIDER="twilio"
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID="invalid_sid"
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN="invalid_token"
